name: WOODY JUMPSCARE!
description:
WANNA SCARE THE POOPOO OUT OF YOUR FRIENDS? IF YES, YOU'VE CAME TO THE RIGHT PLACE! IF NO, GET OUT OF HERE NOW!

With this life changing jumpscare game, you just might need a change of clothes! This game was made using the Godot Game Engine.

CREDITS:
  • Woody model by tobytinker on sketchfab.
  • For the music I used Poles1469 by Trippie Redd ft. 6ix9ine but without the OBNOXIOUS singing.
"Thanks to this game, my nan doesn't have to buy brown paint for the walls! AMAZING!" - Andy Davis
